Drop Geant4::G4visHepRep from the G4Base link list.

HepRep visualization (G4visHepRep) was removed in Geant4 11.0; conda-forge
ships Geant4 11.4.2 (the release floor was 11.2.2), so the target does not
exist and cet_make_library's target_link_libraries fails. All other Geant4
vis targets nug4 links (G4VRML, G4ToolsSG, G4vis_management, ...) remain.
